1775834520220012	bones-dev	itc:v3:AWKSZJkkk5JkmZMxAAAAQatWqrq1bWwAAAE3hww		item.comment	bn-2ury	{"body":"Workspace up, claim held, profile.bench pinned to opt-level=3 (workspace was measuring under opt-level=z all along). Large_repo Tier M baseline: list=789µs, incremental=4.1ms, full_rebuild=4.76s. Triage bench added: pagerank/10k=64.7ms (superlinear vs 1k=708µs), normalize/10k=39.9ms, composite is not hot. Found: no rayon anywhere, pagerank recomputes out-degree per iter, dangling branch is O(n). Operations bench running. Next: write BASELINE.md + flamegraph script + commit."}	blake3:oBjaOvlX0aPdcIUPlCXRUs5DIcY8xavqzJsnZlmeMng
