1777125564026276	bones-dev	itc:v3:AWKSZJkkk5JkmZMxAAAAQatWqrq1bWwAAAE3sQw		item.comment	bn-fu51	{"body":"Fixed in b59643016c9b: TUI search now keeps direct bone ID matches in ranked list search and the standalone search view explicitly merges full/partial ID matches. Verified with just check (fmt, clippy, workspace tests) using LD_LIBRARY_PATH for libssl.so.3."}	blake3:_KbDw2xlDgT4eAWkcANXiJn5bmKqTtci4fDlUpvDYqI
