1777307773611137	bones-dev	itc:v3:AWKSZJkkk5JkmZMxAAAAQatWqrq1bWwAAAE3xAw		item.create	bn-jqv1	{"description":"Bump 0.24.1 -> 0.24.2.\n\nIncludes:\n- feat: default bn binary to mimalloc (b72f2e39) — fixes long-running TUI RSS bloat (1.3+ GB on glibc) by switching to an allocator that returns freed pages to the OS.\n- fix: hint at --fix in 'bn doctor' missing-manifest output (123e9651) — surfaces the existing repair path so users don't need 'bn verify --regenerate-missing'.","kind":"task","title":"release v0.24.2"}	blake3:J8ga0H82yZBDNUM86OJ6dhA7SVRUKqZFQ6lpWVtLi_U
